# ğŸ§® Count Skill 

**CountSkill** is a simple skill for [Open Voice OS (OVOS)](https://openvoiceos.org) that counts from 1 to any user-specified number â€” or even infinitely â€” speaking each number aloud. It supports both **cardinal** and **ordinal** formats and works offline thanks to `ovos-number-parser`.

> ğŸ’¡ this skill was made with the purpose of testing the stop pipeline and showing how to use `ovos-number-parser`

