## ğŸ”§ Features

* ğŸ“¢ Speaks numbers up to a given limit or infinitely
* ğŸ”¢ Supports cardinal (e.g., one, two) and ordinal (e.g., first, second) formats
* ğŸŒ Multilingual support (depending on the configured language)
* ğŸ“´ Fully offline capable â€” no internet required
* ğŸ›‘ Responds to stop requests mid-count
* ğŸ§  Intelligent number extraction from natural language

